title: Identity Crisis HC
description:
Scan of the Hard Cover edition of the best selling and controversial 2004 DC Comics limited series, Identity Crisis. Written by Brad Meltzer and the artistic team of penciler Rags Morales and inker Michael Bair.

Sue Dibny, the Elongated Man's wife, is murdered, her body horribly burned. The DC superhero community rallies to find the murderer.



Released on http://ComicPirates.info
